graph TD
    A[User Clicks 'Add Test Claim' Button] --> B[Frontend Calls createClaim Method]
    B --> C[API Service Sends POST Request to /claims Endpoint]
    C --> D[Backend Receives Request at ClaimsController]
    D --> E[Controller Passes Data to ClaimsService]
